data.description: Welcome home to Lago Mar! This move-in ready home features beautiful entryway with soaring ceilings. Spacious kitchen with 42" cabinets and granite countertops opens to family room. This energy efficient home features upgrades throughout including study with French doors, grand wood entry and premium elevation. Relax in your private backyard under the covered patio and no back neighbors.     This master-planned community features a 12-acre Crystal Lagoon and Recreation Center with a gym, playground, splash pad and resort-style pools. Zoned to Dickinson ISD. Easy access to Hwy 6 and I-45 and just minutes from shopping at Tanger Outlets, restaurants and entertainment.
